gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 117, Spurs 106
gameRecap.excerpt: Denver defeats San Antonio, 117-106. For Denver, Nikola Jokic led the way with 31 points, seven rebounds, five assists, and two blocks while aided by Jamal Murray (15 points, 10 rebounds, eight assists, three steals) in the victory. Jeremy Sochan finished with 19 points, six rebounds, and four assists with Victor Wembanyama adding 17 points, nine rebounds, two steals, and three blocks for San Antonio in the losing effort. Denver improves to 47-20, while San Antonio moves to 14-53 in the loss.
